### ===============================================
### 5. Listar Todas as Readlists do UsuГЎrio
### ===============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/readlists
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===============================================
### 6. Buscar Readlist EspecГ­fica
### ===============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/readlists/{{readlistId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===============================================
### 7. Listar Readlists PГєblicas de um UsuГЎrio
### (NГЈo precisa ser o mesmo usuГЎrio autenticado)
### ===============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/readlists/public/{{username}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===============================================
### 8. Atualizar Nome da Readlist
### ===============================================
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/readlists/{{readlistId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "FicГ§ГЈo CientГ­fica - Atualizado"
}

### ===============================================
### 9. Atualizar DescriГ§ГЈo da Readlist
### ===============================================
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/readlists/{{readlistId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "descricao": "Nova descriГ§ГЈo mais detalhada sobre esta readlist incrГ­vel"
}

### ===============================================
### 10. Tornar Readlist PГєblica
### ===============================================
