### ===============================================
### 16. Adicionar Livro na Readlist
### ===============================================
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/readlists/{{readlistId}}/livros/{{livroId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===============================================
### 17. Remover Livro da Readlist
### ===============================================
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/readlists/{{readlistId}}/livros/{{livroId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===============================================
### 18. Deletar Readlist
### ===============================================
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/readlists/{{readlistId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===============================================
### TESTES DE VALIDAГ‡ГѓO (devem retornar erro)
### ===============================================

### вќЊ Teste: Criar readlist sem nome (deve retornar 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/readlists
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "descricao": "Readlist sem nome"
}

### вќЊ Teste: Nome vazio (deve retornar 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/readlists
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": ""
}

### вќЊ Teste: URL de capa invГЎlida (deve retornar 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/readlists
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Teste URL InvГЎlida",
  "capa_url": "not-a-valid-url"
}

### вќЊ Teste: Buscar readlist inexistente (deve retornar 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/readlists/000000000000000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### вќЊ Teste: Buscar com ID invГЎlido (deve retornar 400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/readlists/invalid-id
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### вќЊ Teste: Sem autenticaГ§ГЈo (deve retornar 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/readlists
Content-Type: application/json

### вќЊ Teste: Token invГЎlido (deve retornar 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/readlists
Authorization: Bearer token_invalido_aqui
Content-Type: application/json

### вќЊ Teste: Atualizar readlist inexistente (deve retornar 404)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/readlists/000000000000000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Tentativa de atualizar"
}

### вќЊ Teste: Deletar readlist inexistente (deve retornar 404)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/readlists/000000000000000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### вќЊ Teste: Adicionar livro com ID invГЎlido (deve retornar 400)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/readlists/{{readlistId}}/livros/invalid-livro-id
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### вќЊ Teste: Remover livro inexistente (deve retornar 404 ou 400)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/readlists/{{readlistId}}/livros/000000000000000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### вќЊ Teste: Buscar readlists pГєblicas de usuГЎrio inexistente (deve retornar 404 ou [])
GET {{baseUrl}}/readlists/public/usuario_inexistente_123
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

